      <title>全球需求担忧加剧，油价维持在 1 月低点附近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-22</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对美国经济放缓和 2025 年前景疲软的担忧抵消了库存下降带来的提振，油价稳定在 1 月份以来的最低收盘价附近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-22</guid>
